Chapter 3 - Server sided Step 1: Anyway move the com folder directly in the bin folder(or whatever your output folder is). The same place data and palidino76 are. There is no need to put it into the src folder first because the files do not need to be compiled. So straight to the bin folder for them. Take SQL.java and put it into the io folder of src. so its ServerName>src>palidino76>rs2>io>SQL.java
